          <a href="https://www.houzz.com/pro" rel="nofollow sponsored" class="btn">Try Houzz Pro</a>
        </div>

        <h2>Key features for masonry software</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Unit-based estimating:</strong> Price by the brick/block/square foot with waste factors</li>
          <li><strong>Material procurement:</strong> Manage deliveries — the wrong block arriving on day 3 of a 5-day job is a disaster</li>
          <li><strong>Crew time tracking:</strong> Masonry is labor-intensive; accurate time tracking is essential to knowing your real costs</li>
          <li><strong>Photo documentation:</strong> Before/during/after photos protect you from disputes about scope and quality</li>
          <li><strong>Change order management:</strong> Added courses, design changes, and extra work need documented approval before you do it</li>
        </ul>

